%% Diagram: Fencing token rejects stale write
%% Type: sequence
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    participant C1 as Client 1
    participant L as Lock Service
    participant S as Storage
    participant C2 as Client 2

    C1->>L: Acquire(resource)
    L-->>C1: Granted, token = 33
    Note over C1: GC pause (lease expires)

    C2->>L: Acquire(resource)
    L-->>C2: Granted, token = 34

    C2->>S: Write (token = 34)
    S-->>C2: OK (highest seen = 34)

    Note over C1: GC ends
    C1->>S: Write (token = 33)
    S-->>C1: REJECTED (33 < 34)
    Note over S: Stale write fenced out
